snippet.title: Doom Warrior Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.doomwarrior.com

Launch trailer for Doom Warrior, a barbaric PvP dueling game for PC, Mac, Linux Android & iOS. Crush your enemies, watch them beg for death and hear the cries of their women!
